0They%20Beat%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan%20will%20have%20their%20task%20cut%20out%20when%20they%20face%20arch-rivals%20India%20in%20their%20second%20match%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Babar%20Azam%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F59905-mohammad-babar-azam-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBabar%20Azam%3C%2Fa%3E-led%20side%20will%20look%20to%20bounce%20back%20from%20their%20shocking%20defeat%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20USA%20on%20Thursday%20in%20Dallas.%20However%2C%20Pakistan's%20hopes%20of%20making%20it%20to%20the%20Super%208%20might%20take%20a%20hit%20if%20they%20lose%20to%20India%20in%20New%20York%20on%20Sunday.%20India%20had%20kicked%20off%20their%20campaign%20with%20a%20routine%20hammering%20of%20Ireland%20at%20the%20same%20venue%20on%20Wednesday.%20With%20the%20USA%20also%20boasting%20a%20100%20percent%20record%20so%20far%2C%20Pakistan%20cannot%20afford%20another%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20things%20stand%2C%20Ireland%20sit%20top%20of%20Group%20A%20with%204%20points%20in%20two%20matches.%20Their%20Net%20Run%20Rate%20is%20%2B0.62.%20Behind%20them%20are%20India%20with%20two%20points%20so%20far%2C%20but%20they've%20only%20played%20one%20game%20so%20far%2C%20while%20their%20Net%20Run%20Rate%20is%20pretty%20impressive%20(%2B3.06).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%20are%20third%20with%20two%20points%20from%20as%20many%20matches%2C%20having%20beaten%20Ireland%20after%20the%20loss%20to%20USA%20in%20the%20tournament%20opener.%20Pakistan%20and%20Ireland%20are%20fourth%20and%20fifth%20with%20no%20points%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPakistan's%20Qualification%20Scenarios%20For%20T20%20World%20Cup%20Super%208%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20can%20still%20miss%20out%20on%20Super%208%20qualification%20even%20if%20they%20win%20all%20of%20their%20remaining%20games.%20Having%20said%20that%2C%20if%20Pakistan%2C%20India%20and%20USA%20all%20finish%20the