rtment%20on%20January%207%2C%202016.%20The%20raid%20targeted%20a%20prominent%20liquor%20businessman%20with%20operations%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20and%20Rajasthan.%20The%20operation%20uncovered%20over%20Rs%201%2C000%20crores%20of%20undeclared%20income%2C%20along%20with%20substantial%20amounts%20of%20cash%2C%20jewellery%2C%20real%20estate%2C%20and%20investments%20in%20various%20enterprises%2C%20including%20colleges%20and%20cold-storage%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20pivotal%20piece%20of%20evidence%20in%20the%20investigation%20is%20a%20coded%20diary%20discovered%20during%20the%20raid.%20This%20diary%20details%20suspicious%20financial%20transactions%20and%20has%20allegedly%20implicated%20several%20Excise%20Department%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspector%20Kavindra%20Singh%20Chauhan%20of%20the%20Special%20Police%20Establishment%20(Lokayukta)%20has%20issued%20a%20notice%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20is%20with%20NDTV%2C%20to%20the%20Excise%20Department%20seeking%20details%20about%20postings.%20Information%20has%20also%20been%20requested%20about%20officers%20stationed%20in%20Gwalior%2C%20Shivpuri%2C%20and%20other%20locations%20during%20the%20period%20under%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717900740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Far00tm9g_police-generic_625x300_10_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcoded-diary-broken-names-lokayukta-probes-madhya-pradesh-liquor-scam-5848131%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Lokayukta%20has%20launched%20an%20investigation%20into%20an%20alleged%20massive%20liquor%20scam%20based%20on%20a%20confidential%20report%20from%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcoded-diary-broken-names-lokayukta-probes-madhya-pradesh-liquor-scam-5848131%22%2C%22