ed%20with%20players%20who%20used%20to%20have%20passion%20and%20gave%20a%20fight%20right%20till%20the%20end.%20This%20team%20gives%20us%20a%20good%20news%20every%203%20months%20for%20the%20last%206-7%20years.)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202009-T20%20World%20Cup%20champion%20further%20stated%20that%20the%20internal%20politics%20in%20domestic%20cricket%20has%20caused%20the%20downfall%20of%20Team%20Pakistan's%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDomestic%20mein%20apni%20siyasat%20chal%20rahe%20hai.%20Apne%20pasand%20ke%20ladke%20la%20rahe%20hai.%20Aapne%20department%20cricket%20regional%20cricket%20bandh%20kar%20ke%20Pakistan%20cricket%20ka%20beda%20gark%20kar%20di.%20India%20number%201%20kyu%20hai%2C%2036%20team%20thi%20%2C%2043%20kar%20din.%20Unhone%20teamein%20badhai%20taaki%20quality%20humare%20paas%20aa%20jaye.%20Yaha%20pe%20saal%20mein%208%20match%20karwate%20hai.%20who%20bhi%20saari%20team%20nahi%20khelte.%20(They%20are%20carrying%20their%20own%20agenda%20in%20domestic%20cricket%20by%20bringing%20the%20players%20of%20their%20preference.%20They%20have%20stopped%20regional%20and%20departmental%20cricket%20and%20almost%20destroyed%20Pakistan%20cricket.%20Why%20is%20India%20no.%201%20right%20now.%20They%20have%20increased%20their%20teams%20from%2036%20to%2043%20to%20get%20more%20quality%20players.%20Here%20they%20play%20only%20matches%20and%20that%20too%20the%20full%20teams%20do%20not%20play.)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20will%20now%20be%20squaring%20off%20against%20the%20arch-rivals%20India%20for%20their%20next%20Group%20A%20match%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20on%20Sunday%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717899900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fq21daurg_kamran-akmal_625x300_09_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fhar-3-mahine-mein-khushkhabri-teary-eyed-kamran-akmal-slams-pakistan-team-5844263%22%2