owled%20out%20for%20a%20sub-100%20total.%20The%20ICC%20had%20to%20issue%20a%20statement%20acknowledging%20the%20inconsistent%20nature%20of%20the%20tracks.%20%26quot%3BNew%20York%20is%20not%20our%20home%20ground.%20We%20have%20played%20two%20matches%20here%20but%20we%20don't%20have%20much%20awareness%20about%20its%20nature.%20It%20behaves%20differently%20on%20different%20days%2C%20so%20even%20the%20curator%20is%20confused%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20said%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20game%20against%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20you%20can%20imagine%20the%20kind%20of%20thinking%20we%20need%20to%20put%20in.%20We%20don't%20know%20on%20which%20pitch%20we%20are%20playing%20(against%20Pakistan)%2C%20so%2C%20whoever%20plays%20better%20cricket%20will%20win%20the%20match%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20slowness%20of%20the%20outfield%2C%20Rohit%20said%2C%20has%20compounded%20the%20worries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20outfield%20is%20slow.%20Some%20shots%20get%20lot%20of%20bounce%20on%20the%20field%2C%20and%20some%20others%20do%20not%20roll%20on%20the%20field.%20So%20running%20between%20the%20wickets%20is%20important.%20We%20need%20to%20play%20as%20per%20conditions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20skipper%20said%20such%20external%20factors%20can%20be%20neutralised%20by%20playing%20good%20cricket%20and%20his%20teammates%20often%20thrive%20in%20tough%20situations.%20The%20Indians%20will%20also%20be%20the%20more%20confident%20unit%20as%20Pakistan%20are%20coming%20off%20stunning%20loss%20to%20tournament%20debutants%20USA%20in%20their%20lung-opener.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlaying%20good%20cricket%20holds%20the%20key%2C%20not%20opposition%2C%20not%20pitch.%20Yes%2C%20it's%20tough%20but%20that's%20why%20I%20would%20like%20to%20highlight%20the%20experience%20we%20have.%20The%20blows%20count%20for%20nothing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rohit%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20hits%20he%20and%20Rishabh%20Pant%20took%20in%20their%20tournament-opener%20against%20Ireland%20due%20to%20the%20uneven%20bounce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20come%20up%20against%20some%20seriously%20quick%20Pakistan%20fast%20bowlers%20such%20as%20Shaheen%20Shah%20Afridi%20and%20Haris%20Rauf%20on%20Sunday%2C%20but%20Rohit%20drew%20comfort%20from%20the%20team's%20past%20experience%20of%20playing%20in%20pace-friendly%20countries%20like%20Australia%20and%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20play%20in%20places%20like%20South%20Africa%2C%20and%20Australia%2C%20we%20have%20to%20overcome%20the%20challenges.%20Gabba%20Test%20is%20one%20big%20example.%20We%20thrive%20in%20these%20difficult%20moments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20World%20Cup%20so%20nothing%20can%20get%20bigger%20than%20this.%20The%20blows%20can%20be%20secondary%20and%20putting%20the%20team's%20cause%20comes%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rohit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbaikar%20hinted%20that%20Rishabh%20Pant%20will%20continue%20to%20bat%20at%20No.%203%20as%20he%20did%20against%20Ireland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20look%20at%20Rishabh%20in%20the%20few%20games%20in%20IPL%20to%20make%20up%20my%20mind%20on%20where%20he%20will%20bat%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20have%20always%20had%20an%20edge%20over%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20World%20Cups%2C%20but%20Rohit%20was%20not%20ready%20to%20rest%20on%20the%20past%20records.%20But%20he%20also%20insisted%20that%20there%20is%20no%20additional%20pressure%20playing%20against%20the%20arch-rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20changes.%20We%20have%20played%20them%20seven%20months%20back%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20and%20(ODI)%20World%20Cup.%20But%20T20%20is%20unpredictable.%20That's%20what%20T20%20cricket%20is%20all%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLast%20World%20Cup%2C%20Pakistan%20lost%20to%20Zimbabwe%20but%20ended%20up%20playing%20the%20final.%20On%20your%20day%20anyone%20can%20beat%20anyone%2