%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20speech%20later%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20said%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20had%20sought%20the%20mandate%20solely%20in%20his%20name%20to%20the%20exclusion%20of%20both%20his%20party%20and%20its%20allies%2C%20but%20has%20suffered%20a%20political%20and%20moral%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20reality%2C%20he%20has%20lost%20the%20mandate%20he%20sought%20and%20thereby%20has%20lost%20the%20right%20to%20leadership%20as%20well.%20Yet%2C%20far%20from%20taking%20responsibility%20for%20the%20failure%2C%20he%20intends%20to%20get%20himself%20sworn%20in%20again%20tomorrow.%20We%20do%20not%20expect%20him%20to%20change%20the%20substance%20and%20style%20of%20his%20governance%2C%20nor%20take%20cognisance%20of%20the%20will%20of%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20why%2C%20as%20members%20of%20the%20CPP%2C%20we%20have%20a%20special%20obligation%20to%20be%20watchful%2C%20vigilant%20and%20proactive%20in%20holding%20him%20and%20his%20new%20NDA%20government%20accountable.%20No%20longer%20can%20and%20should%20the%20Parliament%20be%20bulldozed%20like%20it%20has%20been%20for%20a%20decade%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonia%20Gandhi%20said%20no%20longer%20will%20the%20writ%20of%20the%20ruling%20establishment%20be%20permitted%20to%20disrupt%20Parliament%2C%20whimsically%20mistreat%20members%20or%20push%20through%20legislation%20without%20due%20and%20proper%20consideration%20and%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20longer%20can%20and%20should%20parliamentary%20committees%20be%20ignored%20or%20bypassed%20like%20they%20have%20been%20since%202014.%20No%20longer%20will%20Parliament%20be%20muzzled%20and%20stifled%20as%20it%20has%20been%20over%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CPP%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObserving%20that%20the%20times%20ahead%20were%20challenging%2C%20she%20told%20the%20Congress%20MPs%20that%20they%20have%20to%20be%20alert%20to%20prevent%20any%20attempts%20to%20increase%20polarisation%20and%20erosion%20of%20secular%20and%20democratic%20values%20enshrined%20in%20our%20Constitution%20by%20the%20ruling%20dispensation.%20All%20such%20attempts%20have%20to%20be%20thwarted%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20she%20is%20deeply%20conscious%20of%20the%20responsibility%20all%20have%20placed%20on%20her%20once%20again%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20very%20emotional%20moment%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%20She%20said%20she%20has%20received%20immense%20love%20and%20affection%20from%20the%20party%20leaders%20and%20assured%20them%20saying%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20do%20my%20best%20and%20more%20to%20fulfil%20the%20trust%20and%20confidence%20you%20have%20continued%20to%20place%20in%20me%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20described%20this%20as%20a%20renewed%20opportunity%20for%20the%20party%20that%20established%20parliamentary%20democracy%20in%20the%20country%20to%20bring%20parliamentary%20politics%20back%20on%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20election%2C%20the%20people%20have%20voted%20decisively%20to%20reject%20the%20politics%20of%20divisiveness%20and%20authoritarianism.%20They%20have%20voted%20to%20strengthen%20parliamentary%20politics%20and%20safeguard%20our%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20voted%20for%20the%20agenda%20of%20economic%20and%20social%20justice.%20That%20indeed%20should%20continue%20to%20be%20our%20objective%20and%20guide%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPP%20chairperson%20also%20said%20the%20Congress%20is%20being%20bolstered%20by%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20numbers%20in%20Parliament%20have%20increased%20significantly.%20Not%20only%20is%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20a%20large%20contingent%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20but%20also%20we%20are%20bolstered%20by%20the%20strength%20of%20our%20INDIA%20partners%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20have%20themselves%20come%20back%20impressively%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20yatras%20were%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%20movements%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20(Gandhi)%20deserves%20special%20thanks%20for%20his%20tenacity%20and%20determination%20to%20fight%20on%20in%20the%20face%20of%20unprecedented%20personal%20and%20political%20attacks.%20He%20also%20shaped%20our%20narrative%20on%20guarantees%20and%20protection%20of%20the%20Constitution%20very%20sharply%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Gandhi%2C%20however%2C%20cautioned%20the%20MPs%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20reflect%20on%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20to%20improve%20the%20party's%20position%20in%20the%20states%20where%20its%20performance%20has%20been%20below%20expectation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20congratulated%20the%20newly%20elected%20MPs%2C%20saying%20they%20fought%20a%20tough%20election%20under%20the%20most%20challenging%20circumstances.%20They%20surmounted%20many%20obstacles%20and%20campaigned%20effectively%2C%20she%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20success%20has%20given%20us%20a%20much%20greater%20presence%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20a%20more%20effective%20voice%20in%20its%20proceedings%2C%20both%20of%20which%20will%20help%20give%20greater%20strength%20to%20our%20participation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20lauded%20the%20party's%20campaign%20where%20everyone%20functioned%20truly%20as%20a%20collective%20(body).%20To%20those%20who%20contested%20but%20lost%20this%20election%2C%20she%20extended%20full%20support%20saying%20they%20fought%20valiantly%20and%20did%20the%20party%20proud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonia%20Gandhi%20thanked%20the%20Congress%20workers%20who%20stood%20by%20the%20party%20in%20the%20most%20difficult%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20salute%20their%20courage%20and%20commitment.%20We%20owe%20them%20a%20debt%20of%20gratitude%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20Congress%20has%20once%20again%20demonstrated%20its%20resilience.%20It%20was%20up%20against%20a%20%26quot%3Bmighty%20and%20malevolent%20machine%26quot%3B%20that%20was%20doing%20its%20utmost%20to%20destroy%20the%20party%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20tried%20to%20cripple%20us%20financially.%20It%20carried%20out%20a%20campaign%20against%20us%20and%20our%20leaders%20that%20was%20full%20of%20lies%20and%20defamation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonia%20Gandhi%20lauded%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge's%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20wrote%20our%20obituaries.%20But%20under%20the%20determined%20leadership%20of%20Khargeji%2C%20we%20persevered.%20He%20is%20an%20inspiration%20to%20all%20of%20us.%20His%20commitment%20to%20the%20party%20organisation%20is%20truly%20extraordinary%20and%20we%20all%20have%20to%20learn%20from%20his%20example%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20later%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20big%20thing%20that%20she%20(Sonia%20Gandhi)%20has%20been%20elected%20as%20Congress%20Parliamentary%20Party%20chairperson.%20She%20will%20continue%20to%20guide%20us.%20She%20continues%20to%20serve%20the%20party%20and%20I%20salute%20her%20for%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717871640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fv96910oo_sonia-gandhi-mallikarjun-kharge_625x300_08_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-results-political-and-moral-defeat-of-pm-sonia-gandhi-5848210%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20Parliamentary%20Party%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20on%20Saturday%20described%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20results%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20and%20moral%20defeat%26quot%3B%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%2C%20she%20said%2C%20has%20lost%20the%20moral%20right%20to%20leadership.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-results-political-and-moral-defeat-of-pm-sonia-gandhi-5848210%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-results-political-and-moral-defeat-of-pm-sonia-gandhi-5848210%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-results-political-and-moral-defeat-of-pm-sonia-gandhi-5848210%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2230%20Ministers%20To%20Take%20Oath%20As%20Modi%203.0%20To%20Be%20Sworn%20In%20Today%3A%20Sources%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPM%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20take%20oath%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20the%20third%20straight%20term%20today%20and%20while%20the%20entire%20council%20of%20ministers%20will%20not%20be%20sworn%20in%2C%20nearly%2030%20ministers%20will%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%20The%20strength%20of%20the%20full%20council%20of%20ministers%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20between%2078%20and%2081.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETaking%20oath%20after%20PM%20Modi%20will%20be%20the%20top%20ministers%20of%20the%20government%2C%20including%20those%20who%20will%20hold%20the%20crucial%20portfolios%20of%20home%2C%20defence%2C%20finance%20and%20external%20affairs%20-%20all%20of%20which%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20held%20by%20the%20BJP.%20Others%20who%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20sworn%20in%20will%20include%20those%20who%20will%20be%20entrusted%20with%20critical%20infrastructure%20ministries%20like%20steel%2C%20civil%20aviation%20and%20coal.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20official%20time%20of%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20is%207.15%20to%208%20pm%2C%20which%20means%20that%20it%20is%20expected%20to%20last%2045%20minutes.%20The%20ministers%20that%20will%20be%20taking%20oath%20are%20expected%20to%20get%20calls%20from%20the%20government%20beginning%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20short%20of%20a%20majority%20on%20its%20own%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%2010%20years%20and%20this%20will%20reflect%20in%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20and%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20cabinet.%20Allies%2C%20especially%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20Janata%20Dal%20United%2C%20are%20pressing%20for%20more%20than%20one%20ministerial%20berth%20and%20other%20parties%20will%20need%20to%20be%20accommodated%20too.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20were%20planning%20to%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20ministers%20going%20forward%20but%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20very%20few%20members%20of%20the%20cabinet%20will%20hold%20more%20than%20one%20portfolio%20in%20third%20iteration%20of%20the%20PM%20Modi-led%20cabinet.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAmong%20the%20leaders%20taking%20oath%20tomorrow%20will%20be%20representatives%20of%20the%20BJP's%20NDA%20allies%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20are%20likely%20to%20get%20key%20ministries.%20Reports%20have%20said%20that%20the%20TDP%20is%20likely%20to%20get%20four%20ministerial%20posts%20and%20the%20JDU%20two%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20if%20all%20of%20them%20will%20be%20sworn%20in%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhen%20PM%20Modi%20takes%20oath%20today%2C%20he%20will%20be%20only%20the%20second%20person%20in%20India's%20history%20to%20be%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20three%20successive%20terms.%20The%20country's%20first%20prime%20minister%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20had%20won%20the%201952%2C%201957%20and%201962%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESeveral%20foreign%20leaders%20will%20be%20attending%20the%20event%2C%20including%20Sri%20Lanka%20President%20Ranil%20Wickremesinghe%2C%20Maldives%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%2C%20Bangladesh%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%2C%20Mauritius%20PM%20Pravind%20Kumar%20Jugnauth%