l%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Not%20Just%20Pics%2C%20Prove%20Adultery%20By%20Evidence%3A%20Court%20Amid%20Deepfake%20Menace%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20era%20of%20deepfakes%2C%20photographs%20placed%20by%20a%20spouse%20alleging%20adultery%20by%20the%20other%20partner%20would%20have%20to%20be%20proved%20by%20way%20of%20evidence%20before%20the%20family%20court%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court's%20observation%20came%20while%20dealing%20with%20a%20man's%20contention%20that%20his%20estranged%20wife%20was%20living%20in%20adultery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20dismissed%20the%20man's%C2%A0appeal%20challenging%20a%20family%20court%20order%20directing%20him%20to%20pay%20Rs%2075%2C000%20as%20maintenance%20to%20his%20wife%20and%20minor%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20counsel%20for%20the%20husband%20drew%20the%20court's%20attention%20to%20certain%20photographs%20of%20his%20wife%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20justices%20Rajiv%20Shakdher%20and%20Amit%20Bansal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20clear%20as%20to%20whether%20the%20respondent%2Fwife%20is%20the%20person%20in%20the%20photographs%2C%20as%20alluded%20to%20by%20the%20counsel%20for%20the%20appellant%2Fhusband.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20may%20take%20judicial%20notice%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20are%20living%20in%20the%20era%20of%20deepfakes%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20this%20is%20an%20aspect%20that%20the%20appellant%2Fhusband%2C%20perhaps%2C%20would%20have%20to%20prove%20by%20way%20of%20evidence%20before%20the%20family%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepfake%20technology%20allows%20for%20the%20creation%20of%20realistic%20videos%2C%20audio%20recordings%2C%20and%20images%20that%20can%20manipulate%20and%20mislead%20viewers%20by%20superimposing%20the%20likeness%20of%20one%20person%20onto%20another%2C%20altering%20their%20words%20and%20actions%2C%20thereby%20presenting%20a%20false%20narrative%20or%20spreading%20misinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20by%20the%20bench%20whether%20this%20averment%20of%20adultery%20found%20mention%20in%20the%20man's%20reply%20to%20his%20wife's%20plea%20under%20the%20Hindu%20Marriage%20Act%2C%20his%20counsel%20conceded%20that%20there%20was%20no%20mention%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20noted%20that%20since%20the%20petition%20instituted%20by%20the%20man%20for%20divorce%20is%20pending%20an%20adjudication%2C%20the%20court%20may%20give%20opportunity%20to%20the%20parties%20to%20place%20their%20evidence%20on%20record%20in%20support%20of%20their%20respective%20cases%20if%20this%20issue%20is%20pressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNotably%2C%20this%20aspect%2C%20which%20is%20vehemently%20pressed%20before%20us%2C%20almost%20as%20a%20measure%20of%20desperation%20to%20wriggle%20out%20of%20the%20obligation%20cast%20in%20the%20impugned%20judgment%2C%20finds%20no%20mention%20in%20the%20impugned%20judgment%20(of%20family%20court)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20high%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man's%20counsel%20claimed%20that%20this%20aspect%20was%20raised%20before%20the%20family%20court%2C%20But%2C%20it%20was%20ignored%20while%20rendering%20the%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20this%20was%20the%20situation%2C%20the%20best%20course%20open%20to%20the%20appellant%2Fhusband%20was%20to%20move%20an%20application%20for%20review%20before%20the%20family%20court.%20However%2C%20no%20such%20measure%20has%20been%20taken%20recourse%20to%20by%20the%20husband%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%2C%20an%20architect%2C%20has%20challenged%20a%20family%20court's%20April%2015%20order%2C%20directing%20him%20to%20pay%20Rs%2075%2C000%20as%20monthly%20maintenance%20to%20his%20estranged%20wife%20and%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20had%20married%20in%202018%20and%20has%20a%20five-year-old%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20told%20that%20the%20wife%20has%20a%20post-graduate%20degree%20but%20is%20currently%20unemployed%20and%20living%20with%20her%20parents%20since%20her%20separation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20woman%20had%20sought%20Rs%202%20lakh%20as%20monthly%20maintenance%2C%20the%20family%20court%20ordered%20the%20man%20to%20pay%20Rs%2075%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717867380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-05%2Ft72t3c1g_delhi-high-court-650_625x300_11_May_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-just-pics-prove-adultery-by-evidence-delhi-high-court-amid-deepfake-menace-5846608%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20era%20of%20deepfakes%2C%20photographs%20placed%20by%20a%20spouse%20alleging%20adultery%20by%20the%20other%20partner%20would%20have%20to%20be%20proved%20by%20way%20of%20evidence%20before%20the%20family%20court%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-just-pics-prove-adultery-by-evidence-delhi-high-court-amid-deepfake-menace-5846608%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-just-pics-prove-adultery-by-evidence-delhi-high-court-amid-deepfake-menace-5846608%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-just-pics-prove-adultery-by-evidence-delhi-high-court-amid-deepfake-menace-5846608%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98The%20Good%20Girls%E2%80%99%20Mexican%20Producer%20Woo%20Films%20and%20Colectivo%20Colmena%20Ink%20Three-Pic%20Deal%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717866529000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FMOSTRO_3.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originI