zed%20and%20the%20animals%20have%20been%20shifted%20to%20a%20cow%20shelter%2C%20the%20police%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAutopsy%20reports%20of%20the%20killed%20men%20were%20awaited%2C%20ASP%20Rathore%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20asked%20doctors%20to%20provide%20a%20brief%20report%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20We%20are%20also%20checking%20the%20CCTV%20footage%20along%20the%20route.%20Till%20now%20we%20have%20no%20evidence%20to%20say%20it%20is%20mob%20lynching.%20Efforts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20identify%20those%20who%20chased%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20injured%20man%20was%20in%20no%20position%20to%20give%20a%20statement%20to%20police%20at%20present%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20bodies%20of%20the%20victims%20had%20external%20injuries%20caused%20by%20assault%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BInjuries%20can%20be%20caused%20if%20they%20had%20fallen%20from%20a%2030-feet%20high%20bridge%20and%20landed%20on%20the%20stones.%20Only%20a%20post-mortem%20report%20can%20tell%20how%20the%20injuries%20were%20caused.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717861440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F0htt5beg_india-police-generic_625x300_23_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-cattle-transporters-found-dead-after-chase-by-mob-in-chhattisgarh-cops-5846835%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20cattle%20transporters%20died%20and%20another%20sustained%20serious%20injuries%20under%20suspicious%20circumstances%20after%20being%20allegedly%20chased%20by%20a%20mob%20in%20Chhattisgarh's%20Raipur%20district%20on%20Friday%2C%20police%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F