quot%3Bsometimes%20last%20only%20for%20a%20day%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20after%20a%20Trinamool%20Parliamentary%20Party%20meeting%20on%20Saturday%2C%20a%20day%20before%20the%20oath-taking%20ceremony%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20ministers%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20also%20said%20her%20party%20will%20not%20be%20attending%20the%20event%20because%20the%20government%20is%20being%20formed%20%26quot%3Billegally%20and%20undemocratically%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20are%20having%20to%20depend%20on%20allies%20this%20time%20-%20especially%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20TDP%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20JDU%20-%20because%20the%20party%20has%20managed%20to%20win%20only%20240%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20just-concluded%20elections%2C%20falling%20short%20of%20the%20majority%20mark%20by%2032.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%20situation%20it%20has%20found%20itself%20in%20after%20achieving%20majorities%20on%20its%20own%20twice%20since%202014%2C%20the%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThose%20who%20spoke%20of%20400%20(Lok%20Sabha%20seats)%20could%20not%20get%20even%20a%20simple%20majority%20on%20their%20own.%20Don't%20think%20just%20because%20INDIA%20has%20not%20staked%20claim%20(to%20form%20a%20government)%2C%20nothing%20will%20happen.%20We%20are%20waiting%20and%20watching%20because%20things%20change.%20Ultimately%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20new%20INDIA%20government%2C%20but%20let%20them%20be%20for%20a%20few%20days.%20Sometimes%2C%20governments%20last%20only%20for%20a%20day...%20Anything%20can%20happen%2C%20who%20knows%20if%20this%20government%20will%20last%20even%2015%20days%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20alliance%20managed%20to%20clinch%20232%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20resurgent%20Congress%20and%20a%20strong%20showing%20by%20allies%20like%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20the%20DMK.%20The%20Trinamool%20is