and%20this%20change%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%20has%20won%2029%20of%20the%20state's%2042%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20up%20from%2022%2C%20while%20the%20BJP's%20tally%20went%20down%20from%2018%20in%202019%20to%2012%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Saturday's%20party%20meeting%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20was%20elected%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20Parliamentary%20Party.%20Sudip%20Bandyopadhyay%20will%20be%20the%20party's%20leader%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20with%20Kakoli%20Ghosh%20Dastidar%20as%20the%20deputy%20leader.%20In%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20the%20party%20will%20be%20led%20by%20Derek%20O'Brien%20again%20and%20first-time%20MP%20Sagarika%20Ghosh%20will%20be%20the%20deputy%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717854900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F192j4708_mamata-banerjee_625x300_29_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsometimes-governments-last-only-a-day-mamata-banerjees-reminder-ahead-of-pm-modis-swearing-in-5846511%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Riding%20high%20on%20her%20party's%20win%20against%20the%20BJP%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20dropped%20a%20strong%20hint%20that%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20could%20take%20over%20the%20reins%20at%20the%20Centre%20soon%2C%20saying%20that%20governments%20%26quot%3Bsometimes%20last%20only%20a%20day.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsometimes-governments-last-only-a-day-mamata-banerjees-reminder-ahead-of-pm-modis-swearing-in-5846511%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsometimes-governments-last-only-a-day-mamata-banerjees-reminder-ahead-of-pm-modis-swearing-in-5846511%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndt