and%20strategy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20newest%20aircraft%20carrier%2C%20which%20just%20completed%20its%20maiden%20sea%20trials%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20substantial%20improvement%20over%20its%20two%20predecessors.%20It's%20a%20modern%20flattop%20boasting%20far%20more%20capability%20than%20China's%20earlier%20takes%20on%20an%20older%20Soviet%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fujian%20clearly%20symbolizes%20China's%20desire%20to%20build%20a%20blue-water%20navy%20able%20to%20project%20power%20across%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%2C%20but%20there%20is%20still%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20to%20be%20done%20before%20it%20can%20field%20aircraft%20carriers%20the%20way%20the%20US%20Navy%20can%20on%20the%20high%20seas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20has%20demonstrated%20an%20ability%20to%20field%20the%20aircraft%20and%20the%20aircraft%20carrier%20platforms%2C%26quot%3B%20Guy%20Snodgrass%2C%20a%20former%20defense%20official%20and%20US%20naval%20aviator%2C%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20has%20yet%20to%20be%20demonstrated%20is%20all%20the%20connective%20tissue%20needed%20to%20use%20these%20platforms%20together%2C%20during%20longer-term%20operations%20at%20sea%2C%20outside%20of%20regional%20support%20centers%2C%20and%20during%20times%20of%20conflict.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20isn't%20starting%20this%20process%20from%20scratch%2C%20though%2C%20and%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20learn%20from%20the%20long%20history%20of%20US%20carrier%20operations%20to%20accelerate%20timelines%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emake%20developing%20that%20%26quot%3Bconnective%20tissue%26quot%3B%20easier.%20Still%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20to%20learn%2C%20and%20some%20of%20it%20can%20only%20be%20picked%20up%20from%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22707a82e8-9e45-4fcc-86dc-63d7c2651bad%5C%22%3ETechnological%20leaps%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22China's%20third%20aircraft%20carrier%2C%20the%20Fujian%2C%20adorns%20co