r%20operations%20that%20can%20only%20be%20gained%20by%20experience%2C%20Spicer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20a%20steep%20learning%20curve%20ahead%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20you%20compare%20what%20they're%20dealing%20with%20to%20what%20we've%20been%20dealing%20with%2C%20we've%20been%20doing%20aircraft%20carrier%20operations%20for%20decades.%20So%20we've%20got%20a%20whole%20cadre%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflight-operations-uss-eisenhower-red-sea-houthis-us-navy-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople%20who%20are%20trained%20and%20have%20experience%20operating%20an%20aircraft%20carrier%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20people%20is%20the%20key%2C%26quot%3B%20Spicer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20limited%20experience%20of%20even%20China's%20senior%20naval%20officers%20in%20this%20area%20makes%20it%20difficult%20to%20gain%20expertise%20and%20train%20new%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223882%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20T-45C%20Goshawk%20training%20aircraft%20attached%20to%20Training%20Air%20Wing%20(TAW)%201%2C%20lands%20aboard%20the%20aircraft%20carrier%20USS%20Gerald%20R.%20Ford%20(CVN%2078)%20during%20flight%20operations%2C%20Sept.%2012%2C%202020.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65dcbf17ce7f1785b2e3e144%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222588%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20T-45C%20Goshawk%20training%20aircraft%20attached%20to%20Training%20Air%20Wing%20(TAW)%201%2C%20lands%20aboard%20the%20aircraft%20carrier%20USS%20Gerald%20R.%20Ford%20(CVN%2078)%20during%20flight%20operations%2C%20Sept.%2012%2C%202020.%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%20photo%20by%20Mass%20Communication%20Specialist%20Seaman%20Anton%20Wendler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EClark%20said%20that%20during%20a%202013%20visit%20to%20San%20Diego%2C%20California%2C%20Adm.%20Wu%20Shengli%2C%20then%20commander%20of%20China's%20Navy%2C%20was%20most%20surprised%20by%20the%20number%20of%20people%20involved%20in%20carrier%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20didn't%20realize%20that%20we%20had%20this%20whole%20cadre%20of%20hundreds%20of%20enlisted%20people%20that%20did%20all%20the%20operation%20of%20the%20systems%2C%20maintenance%2C%20and%20oversight%20of%20the%20actual%20flight%20deck%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20Clark%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20challenge%20China%20is%20likely%20facing%20right%20now%20is%20developing%20a%20sustainable%20model%20for%20cultivating%20a%20workforce%20of%20people%20with%20carrier%20knowledge%20and%20experience%20to%20match%20the%20rate%20at%20which%20it%20wants%20to%20build%20carriers.%20And%20that%20extends%20into%20the%20naval%20aviation%20space%20as%20well%20as%20China%20works%20to%20recruit%20and%20train%20pilots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20also%20faces%20challenges%20with%20how%20to%20defend%20its%20carriers.%20Carrier%20strike%20groups%20are%20an%20instrumental%20element%20for%20not%20only%20projecting%20more%20maritime%20power%2C%20but%20also%20defending%20the%20carrier%20and%20its%20aircraft%20in%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20at%20times%20sailed%20its%20aircraft%20carriers%20with%20older%20Type%20052D%20and%20C%20destroyers%2C%20new%20Type%20055%20destroyers%2C%20frigates%2C%20and%20replenishment%20ships%2C%20but%20the%20integration%20and%20interoperability%20that%20makes%20a%20strike%20group%20effective%20takes%20time%20to%20master.%20The%20US%2C%20however%2C%20routinely%20sails%20strike%20groups%20around%20the%20world%2C%20most%20recently%20committing%20them%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouthi-rebels-didnt-hit-us-aircraft-carrier-as-they-claimed-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eongoing%20battle%20with%20the%20Houthis%20in%20Middle%20Eastern%20waters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a0b1ea5c-5540-4bb6-a91d-bb19c7abcf84%5C%22%3ELearning%20%26quot%3Bthe%