%20important%20part%20of%20the%20family%20throughout%20her%2030%20years%20of%20employment%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Farticles.latimes.com%2F1994-10-24%2Fnews%2Fls-54069_1_thelma-howard%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELA%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20Walt%20often%20referred%20to%20her%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Breal-life%20Mary%20Poppins.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20for%20the%20holidays%2C%20Walt%20Disney%20would%20gift%20her%20shares%20of%20Disney%20stock.%20By%20the%20time%20she%20died%20in%201994%2C%20she%20had%20amassed%20nearly%20%249.5%20million%2C%20and%20the%20fortune%20was%20divided%20among%20her%20surviving%20heirs%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Farchive%2Fsaving-grace-vol-42-no-21%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeople%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHe%20came%20close%20to%20opening%20a%20major%20ski%20resort.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225070%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Walt%20Disney%20uses%20a%20baton%20to%20point%20to%20sketches%20of%20Disneyland%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ef90e06f301e00193e6736%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223802%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWalt%20Disney%20uses%20a%20baton%20to%20point%20to%20sketches%20of%20Disneyland.%3Cp%3EHulton%20Archive%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20Disneyland%20after%20opening%20in%201955%20prompted%20Disney%20to%20set%20his%20sights%20on%20another%20potential%20project%3A%20a%20ski%20resort%20in%20Mineral%20King%20Valley%2C%20near%20California's%20Sequoia%20National%20Park.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20plans%20involved%20creating%20a%20vacation%20spot%20centered%20around%20a%20Swiss-style%20village%20with%20six%20ski%20areas%20and%20the%20capacity%20to%20house%2020%2C000%20people%2C%2014%20ski%20lifts%2C%2010%20restaurants%2C%20two%20hotels%2C%20a%20conference