e-report-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estainless%20steel%20exterior%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22238f9912-7758-4298-af52-8a8cab620e4d%5C%22%3EBut%20is%20it%20safe%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20users%20reacting%20to%20Garvin's%20customization%20raised%20concerns%20that%20the%20car%20could%20be%20a%20road%20safety%20hazard%20if%20the%20truck's%20exterior%20reflected%20headlights%20back%20at%20drivers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20if%20the%20vehicle%20blends%20in%20with%20its%20environment%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eon%20the%20road%20as%20well%20as%20it%20appears%20to%20in%20photos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cybertruck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6663ca5ca2a35d0ca3770315%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20front%20driver's%20side%20of%20Garvin's%20polished%20Cybertruck%20reflects%20its%20immediate%20environment.%3Cp%3ETyson%20Garvin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGarvin%20told%20BI%20he%20had%20similar%20concerns%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-drivers-have-a-blinding-headlight-problem-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrivers'%20headlights%3C%2Fa%3E%20bouncing%20off%20the%20truck's%20tailgate%20when%20driving%20at%20night.%20He%20said%20a%20road%20test%20he%20conducted%20with%20his%20wife%20showed%20that%20the%20tailgate%20only%20reflected%20the%20road%20because%20it%20is%20slightly%20slanted%20downward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20told%20BI%20there%20isn't%20much%20literature%20on%20whether%20reflective%20exteriors%20present%20higher%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReflective%20glare%20may%20pose%20the%20same%20problem%20for%20other%20drivers%20as%20headlight%20glare%2C%20but%20I%20am%20not%20aware%20of%20any%20research%20documenting%20whether%20this%20leads%20to%20or%20is%20associated%20with%20increased%20crash%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20David%20Zuby%2C%20chief%20research%20officer%20for%20the%20Insurance%20Institute%20for%20Highway%20Safety%2C%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnathon%20Ehsani%2C%20a%20research%20director%20at%20Johns%20Hopkins%20Center%20for%20Injury%20Research%20and%20Policy%2C%20told%20BI%20he%20wasn't%20aware%20of%20studies%20that%20revealed%20the%20impacts%20of%20a%20vehicle's%20exterior%20color.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Ehsani%20added%20that%20there%20are%20two%20possible%20%26quot%3Bmechanisms%26quot%3B%20that%20could%20make%20a%20reflective%20Cybertruck%20a%20road%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-text-post-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40technicallymims%2Fpost%2FC74YhsyxwWY%5C%22%20data-text-post-version%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40technicallymims%2Fpost%2FC74YhsyxwWY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20Post%20by%20%40technicallymims%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20View%20on%20Threads%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20regarded%20concerns%20raised%20online%3A%20It's%20certainly%20possible%20that%20reflected%20glare%20from%20the%20vehicle%20can%20temporarily%20blind%20other%20drivers%2C%20Ehsani%20said%2C%20cautioning%20that%20he%20would%20have%20to%20see%20the%20vehicle%20in%20person%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20make%20a%20more%20certain%20conclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGarvin%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20Cybertruck's%20shape%20causes%20sunlight%20to%20reflect%20onto%20the%20ground%20rather%20than%20towards%20other%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221002%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cybertruck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6663d10ae079049018173258%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESunlight%20can%20be%20seen%20reflected%20on%20the%20ground%20by%20Garvin's%20polished%20Cybertruck.%3Cp%3ETyson%20Garvin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20far%20more%20plausible%20scenario%20for%20road%20risks%20is%20not%20unique%20to%20the%20reflective%20Cybertruck%2C%20Ehsani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20far%20more%20plausible%20case%20is%20a%20crash%20mechanism%20that%20is%20far%20more%20common%2C%20that%20people%20crash%20from%20every%20single%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that's%20that%20it%20might%20attract%20attention%20because%20it's%20such%20an%20unusual-looking%20vehicle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEhsani%20co-authored%20a%202013%20study%20published%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jahonline.org%2Farticle%2FS1054-139X(13)00779-9%2Ffulltext%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJournal%20of%20Adolescent%20Health%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20documented%20the%20impact%20of%20a%20distracted%20driver.%20His%20research%20found%20that%20drivers%20are%203.8%20times%20more%20likely%20to%20crash%20if%20they%20divert%20their%20attention%20from%20the%20road%20for%20more%20than%20two%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20issue%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20exotic%20or%20highly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F20-million-dollar-exotic-car-hamilton-collection-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunusual%20vehicles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ehsani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20that%20different%20to%2C%20for%20example%2C%20looking%20at%20a%20billboard%20for%20longer%20than%20you%20need%20to%20or%20even%20messing%20around%20with%20your%20entertainment%20console%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c44427f3-b977-4c5a-a62c-b7f94af90931%5C%22%3E'Asking%20to%20be%20pulled%20over'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20polished%20Cybertruck%20may%20attract%20some%20legal%20burdens%20even%20if%20there%20are%20no%20laws%20regarding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyiannimize-celebrity-car-customizer-car-wrapping-2019-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecustomizing%20a%20vehicle's%20exterior%20color%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMartin%20A.%20Kron%2C%20a%20longtime%20New%20York%20traffic%20court%20attorney%20and%20former%20judge%2C%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20he's%20never%20dealt%20with%20a%20legal%20issue%20for%20a%20car's%20paint%20job%20in%20his%2038%20years%20of%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20having%20a%20car%20with%20an%20outlandish%20color%20attracts%20the%20attention%20of%20everyone%20%E2%80%94%20including%20police%20officers%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20there%20may%20not%20be%20a%20spelled%20out%20legal%20prohibition%20against%20it%2C%20in%20the%20real%20world%2C%20if%20you're%20driving%20a%20customized%20car%2C%20you're%20asking%20to%20be%20pulled%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20Kron%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20officers%20could%20pull%20the%20driver%20over%20and%20sniff%20out%20other%20reasons%20to%20give%20a%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZuby%2C%20the%20chief%20research%20officer%20for%20the%20Insurance%20Institute%20for%20Highway%20Safety%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20car's%20paint%20job%20also%20likely%20has%20no%20impact%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-long-does-a-car-accident-affect-my-insurance-rates%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einsurance%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20insurers%20are%20mostly%20restricted%20to%20using%20past%20experiences%20rather%20than%20%26quot%3Bpredictive%20assessments%26quot%3B%20to%20set%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20unless%20an%20insurer%20had%20somehow%20documented%20that%20shinier%20vehicles%20had%20higher%20losses%20than%20less%20shiny%20ones%2C%20it%20would%20be%20unlikely%20to%20affect%20premiums%20paid%2C%26quot%3B%20Zubu%20said.%20%26quot%3BPlus%2C%20it's%20unclear%20how%20an%20insurer%20would%20know%20that%20an%20insured%20made%20the%20vehicle%20shiny%20after%20purchase.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20unless%20your%20vehicle%20is%20featured%20in%20a%20global%20publication%2C%20of%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-polishing-is-it-safe-legal-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717851361000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665d40e6d0b8e1c832cb165d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-polishing-is-it-safe-legal-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20polished%20Cybertruck%20may%20distract%20other%20drivers%20or%20cause%20headlight%20glare%20but%20there%20are%20no%20regulations%20around%20this%20type%20of%20customization%2C%20experts%20say.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A200%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-polishing-is-it-safe-legal-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20mom%20was%20a%20Russian%20mail-order%20bride.%20Here's%20what%20it%20was%20like%20growing%20up.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224385%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Katya%20Suvorova.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6651c256a961b37edf39fffa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223288%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKatya%20Suvorova.%3Cp%3EPhotographer%20and%20writer%20Anna%20Marie%20Tendler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKatya%20Suvorova's%20mom%20became%20a%20mail-order%20bride%20to%20escape%20post-Soviet%20Russia%20in%20the%201990s.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMail-order%20bride%20arrangements%20often%20gave%20men%20control%2C%20leading%20to%20exploitative%20relationships%2C%20she%20said