%2Fshark-tank-cybersecurity-app-artificial-intelligence-ai-pratyusha-vemuri-online-fraud-transactions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecybersecurity%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ethical%20hacking%20space%20is%20a%20growing%20one%20with%20multiple%20jobs%20opening%20up%20for%20the%20same%20in%20India%20and%20abroad.%20For%20anyone%20interested%20in%20getting%20into%20this%20space%2C%20more%20than%20degrees%2C%20Muneeb%20states%20that%20self-learning%20and%20knowledge%20about%20the%20hardware%2C%20operating%20systems%2C%20and%20networking%20is%20essential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20basic%20computer%20degree%20like%20a%20BCA%20or%20MCA%20or%20BTech%20would%20be%20good%20to%20enter%20into%20this%20field.%20Certifications%20like%20OSCP%20(Offensive%20Security%20Certified%20Professional)%20and%20CEH%20(Certified%20Ethical%20Hacker)%20will%20add%20value%20to%20your%20resume.%20What%E2%80%99s%20more%20important%20is%20to%20learn%20about%20computer%20hardware%2C%20networking%2C%20operating%20systems%20like%20Linux%2C%20programming%20languages%2C%20coding%20languages%20and%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Muneeb%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717510127000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-21-1717502240.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D352024%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Muneeb%20Amin%20Bhat%2C%20a%2022-year-old%20from%20Zungalpora%2C%20Kulgam%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20started%20by%20finding%20security%20breaches%20in%20his%20friends'%20and%20neighbours'%20computers.%20Today%2C%20he%20is%20doing%20this%20for%20over%2060%20international%20organisations%20including%20Apple%20and%20NASA.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Grow%20a%20V