20agriculture%20officer%20which%20meant%20frequent%20transfers%20and%20postings%20in%20rural%20Bihar%2FJharkhand%20where%20electricity%20was%20a%20luxury.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fscuzo2-1717419614.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Scuzo%20specialises%20in%20ice%20popsicles%20and%20gelato%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fscuzo2-1717419614.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fscuzo2-1717419614-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fscuzo2-1717419614-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fscuzo2-1717419614-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fscuzo2-1717419614-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351924%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EScuzo%20specialises%20in%20ice%20popsicles%20and%20gelato%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20rarely%20had%20electricity%20growing%20up%20as%20we%20used%20to%20stay%20in%20Naxal%20areas.%20It%20was%20a%20precarious%20situation%20and%20as%20safety%20itself%20was%20such%20a%20big%20issue%2C%20lack%20of%20electricity%20didn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20be%20a%20big%20problem%20then.%20The%20first%20time%20we%20had%20uninterrupted%20electricity%20was%20when%20I%20was%2012%20years%20old%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gagan%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%2C%20they%20had%20a%20happy%20childhood%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20as%20they%20had%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20in%20Delhi%2C%20he%20became%20a%20shift%20manager%20at%20Pizza%20Hut%20in%202006.%20This%20was%20quickly%20followed%20by%20the%20restaurant%20general%20manager%20post%20in%202008%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20when%20he%20was%20chosen%20as%20the%20best%20manager%2C%20the%20video%20was%20circulated%20to%20Pizza%20Hut%20stores%20across%20the%20world%2C%20which%20led%20to%20his%20next%20stint%20at%20one%20of%20its%20centres%20in%20Afghanistan%20at%20the%20Kandahar%20airfield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20handling%20Pizza%20Hut%2C%20Burger%20King%2C%20Kentucky%20Fried%20Chicken%20(KFC)%20stores%20at%20Kandahar%20as%20a%20general%20manager%20for%202.5%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20stint%20propelled%20his%20career%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20next%20stint%20at%20Gloria%20Jeans%20coffee%20in%20Dubai.%20He%20returned%20to%20India%20to%20build%20a%20company%20called%20Honey%20Hut%2C%20which%20gave%20him%20a%20ground%20up%20idea%C2%A0into%20franchising.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20build%20their%20franchise%20vertically.%20I%20created%2015%20stores%20in%20two%20years%20and%20developed%20their%20Standard%20Operating%20Procedures%20(SOPs)%2C%20how%20to%20work%2C%20what%20to%20do%20and%20what%20not%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20here%20on%2C%20he%20worked%20in%20other%20franchising%20verticals%20at%20the%20Chocolate%20Room%20and%20Rasna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20created%20the%20food%20and%20beverage%20verticals%20at%20Rasna%20as%20they%20wanted%20to%20make%20cafes.%20We%20opened%20over%2070%20stores%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20creating%20brands%20for%20others%2C%20Gagan%20desired%20to%20create%20his%20own%20brand.%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20being%20in%20a%20high%20position%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20make%20my%20own%20decisions.%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20my%20own%20brand%20where%20I%20could%20have%20the%20liberty%20to%20do